description: Lucky Number chooses your lucky number for you whenever you need it. Use it for guidance, lottery numbers, and all of life's major decisions.  You can ask it for a lucky number as many times as you need to and it will always give you an answer.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Lucky Number what is my lucky number
Alexa, tell Lucky Number to tell me my lucky number
Alexa, ask Lucky Number for my lucky number
name: Lucky Number
shortDescription: Lucky Number picks your lucky number for all your number needs.
